{"sections":{"section_rich_text_VG3Rmx":{"type":"section-rich-text","blocks":{"heading_hMgfTt":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"{{ page.title }}","text_size":8,"padding_bottom":16}}},"block_order":["heading_hMgfTt"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"width":"wrapper--full-padded","align_text":"text-left","overlay_opacity":0,"overlay_color":"#000000","show_overlay_text":false,"bg_color":"","color":"","padding_top":50,"padding_bottom":0}},"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"subheading":"","subheading_size":3,"show_title":false,"heading_size":8,"show_content":true,"text_size":4,"align_text":"text-left","width":"wrapper","bg_color":"","color":"","padding_top":50,"padding_bottom":50}},"section_double_JCtaa3":{"type":"section-double","blocks":{"heading_A8yg3j":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"How It All Started","text_size":8,"padding_bottom":16}},"text_fhj9UW":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Golf Print Club was born out of frustration. There was a gap in the market—nobody was making high-quality, affordable golf wall art that really connected with younger athletes. That's when I decided to step up and fill the void. I wasn’t interested in following the typical path. After graduating high school, I skipped college to build something I believed in—a brand that not only creates amazing golf wall art but also fosters a culture where athletes feel inspired, motivated, and connected.<\/p><p><\/p>","text_size":4,"text_style":"font-body","padding_bottom":16}},"text_mtM9n7":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>What started with a few posters and has grown into something much bigger.<\/p>","text_size":4,"text_style":"font-body","padding_bottom":16}},"text_BWA7nP":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>A community that embraces the grind and celebrates every aspect of the sport. Golf Print Club is more than just clothing; it’s a lifestyle and a movement to be the best version of your self.<\/p>","text_size":4,"text_style":"font-body","padding_bottom":50}},"video_fnEtH3":{"type":"video","settings":{"video":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/C0030_1.mp4","video_width":100,"custom_aspect_ratio":false,"aspect_ratio":0.5,"padding_bottom":0}}},"block_order":["heading_A8yg3j","text_fhj9UW","text_mtM9n7","text_BWA7nP","video_fnEtH3"],"custom_css":[".brick__block__image {min-height: none; max-height: 100vh;}"],"settings":{"layout":"is-reversed","height":"image-height","mobile_height":"image-height--mobile","width":"wrapper--full","image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1_e456ac4a-344b-4573-a29d-ee7fb80fe2af.png","image_width":"one-half","text_alignment":"text-left","reverse_blocks":false,"bg_color":"","color":"","show_placeholder":true,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_video_AEAXk8":{"type":"section-video","settings":{"video":"shopify:\/\/files\/videos\/C0030_2.mp4","show_video_popup":false,"video_popup_social":"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc","desktop_height":"screen-height-two-thirds","mobile_height":"screen-height-two-thirds--mobile","width":"wrapper--full","overlay_opacity":30,"overlay_color":"#000000","show_overlay_text":false,"title":"","heading_size":8,"description":"","text_size":3,"flex_align":"align--middle-center","bg_color":"","color":"#ffffff","link_text":"","link":"","button_type":"btn--primary","button_size":"","button_style":"btn--solid","show_arrow":false,"padding_top":30,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_rich_text_columns_3UfeVL":{"type":"section-rich-text-columns","blocks":{"heading_AkQp7i":{"type":"heading","settings":{"position":"left","title":"The Mission","text_size":8,"padding_bottom":16}},"text_EJH7Mk":{"type":"text","settings":{"position":"left","text":"<p>Golf Print Club is built on a simple but powerful idea: to inspire and equip golfers with everything they need to succeed, not just through gear but through media, events, and opportunities. Our mission is to make the sport of golf more exciting, accessible, and meaningful for athletes everywhere, especially those at the high school and young adult levels.<\/p>","text_size":4,"text_style":"font-body","padding_bottom":16}},"heading_whrrUJ":{"type":"heading","settings":{"position":"right","title":"Vision for the Future","text_size":8,"padding_bottom":16}},"text_ML9JqF":{"type":"text","settings":{"position":"right","text":"<p>The long-term vision is to grow beyond apparel. I want to build a brand that plays a major role in the sport—through media, leagues, and events that uplift athletes and give them the recognition they deserve. We’re not just building a business; we’re creating a movement that will grow the sport and make a lasting impact.<\/p>","text_size":4,"text_style":"font-body","padding_bottom":16}}},"block_order":["heading_AkQp7i","text_EJH7Mk","heading_whrrUJ","text_ML9JqF"],"settings":{"width":"wrapper","left_column_width":50,"right_column_width":57,"align_text":"text-right","align_text_mobile":"text-left--mobile","padding_top":100,"padding_bottom":100}},"section_rich_text_4FUqMw":{"type":"section-rich-text","blocks":{"heading_94WVCR":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"Why Us?","text_size":8,"padding_bottom":16}},"text_7pHdYz":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Here’s what makes Golf Print Club different:<\/p>","text_size":4,"text_style":"font-body","padding_bottom":16}}},"block_order":["heading_94WVCR","text_7pHdYz"],"settings":{"width":"wrapper","align_text":"text-center","overlay_opacity":0,"overlay_color":"#000000","show_overlay_text":false,"bg_color":"#2E7D32","color":"#fbfbfb","padding_top":100,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_rich_text_L8abcX":{"type":"section-rich-text","blocks":{"text_TTwQM9":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h6><strong>We Understand Young Athletes:<\/strong> <\/h6><p>- As someone who has been in your shoes, I know what it takes to balance the grind of training, school, and life. Our gear is designed with that same understanding—it’s affordable, high-quality, and built for performance.<\/p><h6><strong>Unique, Purpose-Driven Design:<\/strong> <\/h6><p>- We blend vintage aesthetics with streetwear influences to create gear that’s stylish and functional, so you feel just as good off the track as you do on it.<\/p><h6><strong>More Than Just Gear:<\/strong> <\/h6><p>- Golf Print Club isn’t just about clothes—it’s about building a lifestyle and community that celebrates the love of golf.<\/p><h6><strong>Community-First Approach:<\/strong> <\/h6><p>- From collaborating with athletes to creating engaging content, Golf Print Club is all about fostering connections and growing the sport together.<\/p>","text_size":4,"text_style":"font-body","padding_bottom":16}}},"block_order":["text_TTwQM9"],"settings":{"width":"wrapper","align_text":"text-left","overlay_opacity":0,"overlay_color":"#000000","show_overlay_text":false,"bg_color":"#2E7D32","color":"#fbfbfb","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":100}},"section_slideshow_x4LbnR":{"type":"section-slideshow","blocks":{"image_fgNCeJ":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/4_a1b14917-4468-4134-8976-725f3735867f.png","overlay_opacity":50,"overlay_color":"#000000","show_overlay_text":false,"title":"How We’re Changing the Golf Community","heading_size":7,"description":"","text_size":5,"flex_align_desktop":"align--middle-center-desktop","flex_align_mobile":"align--middle-center-mobile","bg_color":"","color":"#ffffff","first_button_text":"","first_button_link":"","first_button_type":"btn--primary","first_button_size":"","first_button_style":"btn--solid","first_button_show_arrow":false,"second_button_text":"","second_button_link":"","second_button_type":"btn--white","second_button_size":"","second_button_style":"btn--solid","second_button_show_arrow":false}}},"block_order":["image_fgNCeJ"],"settings":{"height":"screen-height-two-thirds","mobile_height":"screen-height-three-quarters--mobile","width":"wrapper--full-padded","transition":"slide","show_arrows":false,"autoplay":false,"autoplay_speed":8,"padding_top":30,"padding_bottom":30}},"section_rich_text_L4gB9H":{"type":"section-rich-text","blocks":{"text_cHqPRX":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>The sport of golf is evolving, and Golf Print Club is at the forefront of that change. Here’s how we’re making an impact:<\/p>","text_size":4,"text_style":"font-body","padding_bottom":16}}},"block_order":["text_cHqPRX"],"settings":{"width":"wrapper","align_text":"text-center","overlay_opacity":0,"overlay_color":"#000000","show_overlay_text":false,"bg_color":"","color":"","padding_top":10,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_text_row_EGc4EF":{"type":"section-text-row","blocks":{"icon_iwtytC":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-shield","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#fbfbfb","title":"Building a Legacy:","heading_size":4,"text":"<p>Golf Print Club isn’t just a brand you wear—it’s a movement you belong to, one that celebrates hard work and motivates you to be your best.<\/p>","text_size":3}},"icon_VBmXLB":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-trophy","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#fbfbfb","title":"Creating a Platform for Athletes and Creators:","heading_size":4,"text":"<p>Whether you’re an elite golfer or just love the sport, Golf Print Club gives you the tools and space to inspire others.<\/p>","text_size":3}},"icon_VeqeGT":{"type":"icon","settings":{"icon_name":"icon-chat","icon_size":20,"icon_color":"#fbfbfb","title":"Expanding into Media and Events:","heading_size":4,"text":"<p>We’re building more than just a brand—we’re laying the groundwork for leagues, events, and content that will elevate the sport.<\/p>","text_size":3}}},"block_order":["icon_iwtytC","icon_VBmXLB","icon_VeqeGT"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_size":5,"layout":"grid","grid":3,"align_heading":"text-left","align_text":"text-left","icon_alignment":"icon--left","align_columns":"flex-align-top","width":"wrapper","bg_color":"","color":"","padding_top":30,"padding_bottom":0,"layout_mobile":"slider"}},"section_rich_text_QaFAxH":{"type":"section-rich-text","blocks":{"heading_pDbwqk":{"type":"heading","settings":{"title":"How You Can Help Us Grow the Movement","text_size":8,"padding_bottom":16}},"text_QnXzRa":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>This journey isn’t just mine—it’s ours. Here’s how you can be part of Golf Print Club and help us build something great:<\/p>","text_size":4,"text_style":"font-body","padding_bottom":16}}},"block_order":["heading_pDbwqk","text_QnXzRa"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"width":"wrapper","align_text":"text-center","overlay_opacity":0,"overlay_color":"#000000","show_overlay_text":false,"bg_color":"#2E7D32","color":"#ffffff","padding_top":30,"padding_bottom":0}},"section_press_logos_LMtbAz":{"type":"section-press-logos","blocks":{"logo_item_LJmjKB":{"type":"logo-item","settings":{"logo_width":100,"link":"","heading":"Represent the brand during your training and races. Every piece of gear you wear helps spread the message.","heading_size":6}},"logo_item_CPj3PV":{"type":"logo-item","settings":{"logo_width":100,"link":"","heading":"Share our content, tag us on social media, and introduce other golfers to the movement.","heading_size":6}},"logo_item_rcampE":{"type":"logo-item","settings":{"logo_width":100,"link":"","heading":"Follow us on socials, join the conversation, and connect with other athletes in the Golf Print Club community.","heading_size":6}},"logo_item_DAje6g":{"type":"logo-item","settings":{"logo_width":100,"link":"","heading":"If you’re a golfer, creator, or just passionate about the sport, we’d love to hear from you. Together, we can grow something amazing.","heading_size":6}}},"block_order":["logo_item_LJmjKB","logo_item_CPj3PV","logo_item_rcampE","logo_item_DAje6g"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"","enable_heading_slider":true,"text_style":"font-body","logo_opacity":25,"bg_color":"#2E7D32","color":"#ffffff","padding_top":30,"padding_bottom":50}},"section_highlights_VtkLy8":{"type":"section-highlights","blocks":{"highlight_paBjXU":{"type":"highlight","settings":{"heading":"Instagram","url":"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/_golf